# ============================================================
# Setor Email Pro — Environment Variables
# ============================================================
# Hanya 2 variabel di bawah ini yang WAJIB diisi di Vercel.
# JWT_SECRET, VITE_APP_ID, VITE_OAUTH_PORTAL_URL, dll
# akan di-generate otomatis jika tidak diisi.
# ============================================================

# ------ WAJIB DIISI ------

# 1. JSONBin.io — Database JSON
#    Cara dapat:
#    a. Buat akun gratis di https://jsonbin.io
#    b. Dashboard → API Keys → Copy "Secret Key"
JSONBIN_API_KEY=$2a$10$oZ0RaGbE3nJmcIOwphl7b.OmMSNn6F.IOgSDMHt2zeGhPJWZz9Dd.

#    c. Buat Bin baru: https://jsonbin.io/app/bins/new
#       Content: {} (JSON kosong)
#    d. Copy BIN ID dari URL (format: 64a1b2c3d4e5f6...)
JSONBIN_BIN_ID=6a3a5a8ada38895dfef0b151

# 2. OAuth Manus SSO
OAUTH_SERVER_URL=https://your-oauth-server.com
OWNER_OPEN_ID=your-open-id

# ------ OPSIONAL (auto-generate jika tidak diisi) ------

# VITE_APP_ID=your-app-id
# VITE_OAUTH_PORTAL_URL=https://your-oauth-portal.com
# JWT_SECRET=auto-generated-if-empty
